and we want them now.

01:09:38.482 --> 01:09:40.848
<i>Miss Blenehassitt, telephone the police.</i>

01:09:40.951 --> 01:09:45.354
It's all right,
Miss Blenehassitt.

01:09:45.455 --> 01:09:49.653
<i>I'm warning you,
if you do, you're fired.</i>

01:09:49.760 --> 01:09:52.250
