and fire you immediately.

01:09:54.797 --> 01:09:59.734
Yes, we'll buy this place, and we'll
install a fucking jukebox in here...

01:09:59.835 --> 01:10:03.362
and liven
all of you stiffs up a bit.

01:10:03.472 --> 01:10:05.838
