01:14:40.933 --> 01:14:43.333
- He's not gonna try anything.
- Of course he is!

01:14:43.435 --> 01:14:47.268
- He means business.
- Anyway, he sent me out to tell you coffee's ready.

01:14:47.371 --> 01:14:50.772
I couldn't drink it. I've got
