01:19:35.776 --> 01:19:39.268
Well, you're in there,

01:19:39.379 --> 01:19:41.847
and I'll take these
and I'll have the couch.

01:19:43.349 --> 01:19:45.783
I'll say good night, then, Monty.

01:19:45.885 --> 01:19:50.117
