01:20:22.386 --> 01:20:25.822
<i>But not that tired, eh?</i>

01:20:30.961 --> 01:20:35.954
- Are you a sponge or a stone?
- What do you mean?

01:20:36.065 --> 01:20:39.557
<i>Do you like to experience
all facets of life?</i>

01:20:39.669 --> 01:20:43.161
