because he couldn't love you.

01:24:34.816 --> 01:24:37.807
<i>He's lying. Lying!</i>

01:24:37.919 --> 01:24:42.185
Oh, my dear boy.

01:24:42.290 --> 01:24:45.418
If I had known that, I would never
